---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Affiliate Disclosure - Online College Courses';
const pageDescription = 'Transparency about our affiliate relationships and how we earn commissions when you enroll in courses through our links.';
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
        <p class="updated-date">Last Updated: February 20, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
          <p>
            At Online College Courses, we believe in complete transparency about our business model and how we make money. This page explains our affiliate relationships and how they may influence the content on our site.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>What Are Affiliate Links?</h2>
          <p>
            Affiliate links are special URLs that allow us to earn a commission when you click on them and enroll in a course or make a purchase. These commissions come from the institutions or platforms, not from you - you pay the same price whether you use our link or go directly to the institution.
          </p>
          
          <div class="callout-box">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Important:</strong> Using our affiliate links costs you nothing extra. The price you pay is exactly the same as going directly to the course provider.
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
          <p>We earn revenue through several methods:</p>
          
          <div class="revenue-list">
            <div class="revenue-item">
              <div class="revenue-icon">1</div>
              <div class="revenue-details">
                <h3>Affiliate Commissions</h3>
                <p>
                  When you click on a course link and enroll, we may receive a commission from the institution or affiliate network. Typical commissions range from 3-15% of the course fee.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="revenue-item">
              <div class="revenue-icon">2</div>
              <div class="revenue-details">
                <h3>Display Advertising</h3>
                <p>
                  We may display advertisements from third-party ad networks. These ads help support our free content and services.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="revenue-item">
              <div class="revenue-icon">3</div>
              <div class="revenue-details">
                <h3>Sponsored Content</h3>
                <p>
                  Occasionally, we may publish sponsored articles or feature specific courses. All sponsored content is clearly labeled as such.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Our Editorial Independence</h2>
          <p>
            While we participate in affiliate programs, this does not influence our editorial decisions or course recommendations. Our reviews and ratings are based on:
          </p>
          <ul class="features-list">
            <li>Actual student reviews and feedback</li>
            <li>Course quality and content</li>
            <li>Institutional accreditation and reputation</li>
            <li>Value for money</li>
            <li>Learning outcomes and career benefits</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We strive to provide honest, unbiased information to help you make informed decisions about your education.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Affiliate Partnerships</h2>
          <p>
            We have affiliate relationships with various educational institutions, online learning platforms, and affiliate networks, including but not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul class="partners-list">
            <li>Individual colleges and universities</li>
            <li>Online course platforms (Coursera, edX, Udacity, etc.)</li>
            <li>Education affiliate networks</li>
            <li>Learning management system providers</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
          <p>
            In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's 16 CFR Part 255 guidelines concerning the use of endorsements and testimonials in advertising, we disclose that we receive financial compensation for some of the products and services mentioned on this website.
          </p>
          <p>
            We only recommend courses and institutions we believe provide genuine value to students. We will never recommend a course solely because it offers a higher commission.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>User Reviews and Ratings</h2>
          <p>
            The reviews and ratings displayed on our site come from real students who have taken these courses. We do not:
          </p>
          <ul class="features-list">
            <li>Pay for positive reviews</li>
            <li>Remove negative reviews (unless they violate our guidelines)</li>
            <li>Manipulate ratings to favor higher-commission courses</li>
            <li>Post fake reviews</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            All reviews are moderated for spam, profanity, and compliance with our review guidelines, but we do not alter the content or ratings provided by genuine users.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Price Changes and Accuracy</h2>
          <p>
            While we strive to keep course information and pricing accurate and up-to-date, prices and course details can change at any time. The final price you pay will be determined by the course provider at the time of enrollment.
          </p>
          <p>
            We are not responsible for any discrepancies between the information displayed on our site and the actual course offerings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Your Trust Matters</h2>
          <p>
            We take our responsibility seriously. Our goal is to help you find the best online courses for your needs while being completely transparent about how we operate.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you ever have questions about our affiliate relationships or editorial practices, please don't hesitate to <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Updates to This Disclosure</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this disclosure from time to time to reflect changes in our business practices or legal requirements. When we make significant changes, we will update the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page.
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="contact-box">
          <h3>Questions About Our Affiliate Program?</h3>
          <p>We're happy to answer any questions about our affiliate relationships or business model.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="contact-button">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 6) 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 calc(var(--spacing) * 3);
  }

  .legal-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 8);
    padding-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--neutral-200);
  }

  .legal-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--neutral-900);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
  }

  .updated-date {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--neutral-600);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .legal-content {
    background: white;
    padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 6);
    border-radius: calc(var(--border-radius) * 1.5);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 6);
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--neutral-900);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2.5);
  }

  .content-section p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--neutral-700);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2.5);
  }

  .content-section a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .content-section a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }

  .callout-box {
    display: flex;
    gap: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
    padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 3);
    background: #dbeafe;
    border: 1px solid #3b82f6;
    border-radius: calc(var(--border-radius) / 2);
    margin: calc(var(--spacing) * 3) 0;
  }

  .callout-box svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #1e40af;
  }

  .callout-box strong {
    color: #1e40af;
  }

  .revenue-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
    margin: calc(var(--spacing) * 4) 0;
  }

  .revenue-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: calc(var(--spacing) * 3);
  }

  .revenue-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .revenue-details h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--neutral-900);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 1);
  }

  .revenue-details p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .features-list,
  .partners-list {
    margin: calc(var(--spacing) * 2) 0;
    padding-left: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
  }

  .features-list li,
  .partners-list li {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--neutral-700);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 1.5);
  }

  .contact-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #0ea5e9 100%);
    padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 5);
    border-radius: calc(var(--border-radius));
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
    margin-top: calc(var(--spacing) * 8);
  }

  .contact-box h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
    color: white;
  }

  .contact-box p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .contact-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 2.5) calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: calc(var(--border-radius) / 2);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .contact-button:hover {
    background: var(--neutral-100);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .legal-content {
      padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
    }

    .revenue-item {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
